abstract: The nonprofit SoHo gallery Artists Space has suspended its programming because it says the landlord is scheduling construction work that would disrupt its exhibitions.
snippet: The nonprofit SoHo gallery Artists Space has suspended its programming because it says the landlord is scheduling construction work that would disrupt its exhibitions.

snippet: The midsize crossover category has gotten smaller with the discontinuation of the Honda Crosstour and Toyota Venza, but the new Edge remains a strong entry.
lead_paragraph: ONE glance at your neighborâ€™s Chevrolet Suburban will confirm that Americans prefer roomier vehicles, so the dwindling number of midsize crossovers is puzzling. Honda Crosstour and Toyota Venza have been discontinued for lack of interest. That leaves the second-generation Ford Edge to do battle with the Sorento, Santa Fe, Murano and perhaps the raised wagon that is Outback.

abstract: With the help of A.I., Americaâ€™s most famous doll tries to fulfill a timeless dream â€” convincing little girls that sheâ€™s a real friend. What will happen if they believe her?
snippet: With the help of A.I., Americaâ€™s most famous doll tries to fulfill a timeless dream â€” convincing little girls that sheâ€™s a real friend. What will happen if they believe her?
lead_paragraph: It looked like a childâ€™s playroom: toys in cubbies, a little desk for doing homework, a whimsical painting of a tree on the wall. A woman and a girl entered and sat down in plump papasan chairs, facing a low table that was partly covered by a pink tarp. The wall opposite them was mirrored from floor to ceiling, and behind it, unseen in a darkened room, a half-dozen employees of the toy company Mattel sat watching through one-way glass. The girl, who looked about 7, wore a turquoise sweatshirt and had her dark hair pulled back in a ponytail. The woman, a Mattel child-testing specialist named Lindsey Lawson, had sleek dark hair and the singsong voice of a kindergarten teacher. Microphones hidden in the room transmitted what Lawson said next. â€˜â€˜You are going to have a chance to play with a brand-new toy,â€™â€™ she told the girl, who leaned forward with her hands on her knees. Removing the pink tarp, Lawson revealed Hello Barbie.

abstract: It may seem counterintuitive, but lifting the restrictions on fundraising by political parties would help.
snippet: It may seem counterintuitive, but lifting the restrictions on fundraising by political parties would help.
lead_paragraph: Nearly everyone in America agrees that there is too much influence-seeking money in politics, except for the people who benefit from it. Public concern over the potential for corruption in this flood of cash has resulted, over the past half century, in five separate approaches to the regulation of campaign finance.

snippet: Dr. Thomas R. Insel announced that he is stepping down after 13 years as director of the National Institute of Mental Health.
lead_paragraph: Dr. Thomas R. Insel, the director of the National Institute of Mental Health, announced on Tuesday that he planned to step down in November, ending his 13-year tenure at the helm of the worldâ€™s leading funder of behavioral-health research to join Google Life Sciences, which seeks to develop technologies for early detection and treatment of health problems.
